Password Cracker

Overview

User can test their password and see if it has been compromised by the hackers.

list = [Aika's password dictionary]

*** Test your password and see if it has been compromissed by hackers ***
	!!! Don't enter your real password !!! 

	Would you like to test your password, Yes or No ? 
		
		if the answer Yes -> check Aika's dictionary for users password -> return the password if matched
		
		elif the answer No -> Good bye! 
		*** Remember, Long password = Strong password ***

		else "That's not an option"


Users can see complexity of thier passwords and get recomendations on to creat stronger password.

	*** I can help you to build a strong password *** 

	Would you like lean how to build the strong password? Yes or No? 
	
	*** Strong Password Tips -> Long Password = Strong Passwword ***

	If the answer = "Yes" -> Enter a password 

		if password =< than 6 characters ->"Your password can be cracked by the time you get your drive-thru order"
		elif password =< than 10 charachters -> "Your passwor can be cracked in the hour you spend doing yoga"
		elif password =< than 14 charachters -> "Your passwor can be cracked by your next birthday"
		elif password => than 15 charactesrs -> "Your password takes longer to crack than raising a child " 

	elif the answer = "No" - > Good Bye. 
	*** Remember, Long password = Strong password ***

	else "That's not an option"



